ed="T" n="0848b04"/><persName key="A012856">釋羅僧</persName>者，<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>聖寺<ptr target="#n2753"/>中得果位人也。甞寢疾<lb
ed="T" n="0848b05"/>於<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>，同會僧人俱不<anchor xml:id="beg0848001"/>測<anchor xml:id="end0848001"/>也，而瞻視之，<lb
ed="T" n="0848b06"/>曾無怠慢。將及九旬而病愈，臨訣之際曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0848b07"/>「深感所苦，而煩看視，今遂平復，由師之力。<lb
ed="T" n="0848b08"/><ref type="person" target="#A012856">我</ref>住在<placeName key="PL000000035743">劍</placeName>外<placeName key="PL000000035032">九隴郡</placeName>之<placeName key="PL000000035013">茶籠山</placeName>爾。異日遊<lb
ed="T" n="0848b09"/>方，無忘相訪也。」暮歲而至<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>，歷訪群峯，<lb
ed="T" n="0848b10"/>遍訊老樵輩，且曰未甞聞茲山名。乃<anchor xml:id="beg0848sgsz1"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0848sgsz1"/>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0848b11"/>「噫，病禪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1808"/>之妄也？」將迴，遇山童曰：「某是彼巖<lb
ed="T" n="0848b12"/>之聚沙者<ptr target="#n516"/>。」即前導而去，俄覩殿塔儼空<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1810"/>，房<lb
ed="T" n="0848b13"/>廊環肅，果值昔之臥病者，迎門敘故。日將<lb
    ed="T" n="0848b14"/>暮矣，而謂之曰：「茲寺非得漏盡通<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1809"/>不能<lb
ed="T" n="0848b15"/>至此。爾以<ref type="person" target="#A012856">我</ref>宿緣一諧遘止。言寄宵乎，斯<lb
ed="T" n="0848b16"/>為未可。爾其克勤修證，至此胡難？」乃命舊<lb
ed="T" n="0848b17"/>童送師歸去。其僧迴望，但見巖壁峭峻，杉檜<lb
ed="T" n="0848b18"/>莽蒼而已，則<date notBefore-iso="+0836-01-26" key="j20264282027904" notAfter-iso="+0840-02-10"><name>開成</name>中</date>也。時<persName key="A000753"><persName>悟達國師</persName><persName>知玄</persName></persName><ptr target="#n2754"/>著<lb
ed="T" n="0848b19"/>傳之次，得僧<persName key="A012857">可思</persName>──尤閑地理<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1811"/>，命為<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>作他<lb
ed="T" n="0848b20"/>日安塋兆之地，得<placeName key="PL000000035013">景丹</placeName>前峯。其山若雉堞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1785"/><lb
ed="T" n="0848b21"/>狀，雖高低起伏，而中砥平。俄有里人耆老<lb
ed="T" n="0848b22"/>曰：「古相傳云<placeName key="PL000000035013">茶籠山</placeName>矣。」</p>
